      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so my back is absolutely killing me right now. i already took 800mg of ibuprofen like an hour ago but it’s not doing anything and i can barely move. can i just take some aspirin on top of it or maybe take another dose of the ibu once this wears off? i really need something to kick in so i can sleep.",
